ia del&nbsp;Azuay &nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://gadbulan.gob.ec/azuay/\\\">https://gadbulan.gob.ec/azuay/</a></td><td rowspan=\\\"8\\\"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>1</p></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Con &nbsp;esta &nbsp;contratación &nbsp;de &nbsp;servicio, &nbsp;nuestra &nbsp;Institución requiere&nbsp;que&nbsp;los&nbsp;iconos&nbsp;de&nbsp;las&nbsp;tareas&nbsp;principales&nbsp;del&nbsp;sitio</p></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>web&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;tengan&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;un&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;diseño&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;de&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;buen&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;contenido,</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>modernización &nbsp;y &nbsp;colores &nbsp;acordes &nbsp;a &nbsp;nuestra &nbsp;imagen</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>institucional&nbsp; &nbsp;pudiendo&nbsp; &nbsp;ser&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;cambiados&nbsp; &nbsp;en&nbsp; &nbsp;cualquier</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>momento&nbsp;sin&nbsp; generar &nbsp;cargos&nbsp;o&nbsp;facturas &nbsp;adicionales&nbsp; &nbsp;al valor&nbsp;contratado&nbsp;de manera&nbsp;anual.</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Uso&nbsp;activo&nbsp;de los servicios de&nbsp;la&nbsp;página web.</p></td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><p>&nbsp;</p><p>•&nbsp;Uso&nbsp;de&nbsp;correo&nbsp;institucional.</p><p>•&nbsp;Espacio&nbsp;Ilimitado.</p><p>•&nbsp;Transferencia&nbsp;ILIMITADA.</p><p>•&nbsp;Cuentas Correo&nbsp;ilimitadas.</p><p>•&nbsp;Bases de&nbsp;Datos Ilimitadas.</p><p>•&nbsp;DominiosIlimitados.</p><p>•&nbsp;Parking&nbsp;Ilimitado.</p><p>•&nbsp;Servicios brindados:</p><p>o&nbsp;Restauración ygeneración&nbsp;de&nbsp;respaldos.</p><p>o&nbsp;Actualizaciones&nbsp;de&nbsp;